UPPARK is the mobile app for parking in Romania. By using UPPARK you can find parking spots and pay the parking fee.
DOWNLOAD THE APP FREE OF CHARGE AND REGISTER


You can register multiple cars, either personal or company cars. You can create a separate
profile for your company car.


FIND A PARKING SPOT
Based on your phone’s GPS location services, the app identifies your location, the close-by parking areas and the number of available parking spots*. You can check the parking fees before choosing your parking spot.


CHOOSE THE PARKING DURATION


Estimate the desired parking duration and select the minimum duration in the app.
You can extend it later.


PAY IN A COMFORTABLE AND SAFE WAY
Choose whether you want to pay using your personal bank card, the company card or by SMS*. Any method is safe.


RECEIVE NOTIFICATIONS IN DUE TIME
It doesn't matter if you tarry, you will receive a notification 10 minutes before your parking term expires. You can extend it as many times as you want, remotely, from your phone.


USE IT IN ANY PARKING PLACE


THE UPPARK mobile app can be integrated and used* anywhere in Romania for on-street parking, as well as for parking lots, multi-storey parking lots, municipal or private parking lots.
You can find the complete and periodically updated list of locations and parking areas where you can use UPPARK at www.uppark.io.


BUSINESS ACCOUNT FOR COMPANIES
Companies have the possibility to register their entire car fleet. They receive reports and invoices. The expenses are under control.


(*where applicable)


WE WANT TO BE EVEN BETTER


We make continuous efforts to improve this app. Please reach out if you experience any issues or if you want to suggest an improvement. You can easily contact us at support@uppark.io.
UPPARK is part of fastPark, a leader on the Romanian market for integrated parking solutions, www.fastPark.ro.
